{"tid":1107131,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"眼見芝娃娃快遭輾斃 邊境牧羊犬飛奔叼走佢","createTime":"2019-04-15T04:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T16:47:10.000Z","uid":71393,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4488e4cd05e3e70ee8cd99a378fb60eb8d3ca243","tid":1107131,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T04:39:40.000Z","msg":"加拿大一隻邊境牧羊犬（Border Collie）勇救一隻芝娃娃，免牠成為輪下亡魂。<br />\n<br />\n閉路電視片段顯示，那隻機警的邊境牧羊犬，在魁北克省東部城市加斯佩（Gaspe）跟另外兩犬在雪地上玩耍，三犬四散之後，一名女司機倒車到雪地，芝娃娃不知汽車向牠方向倒後駛來，只顧跑向對面找牠的玩伴。這時，邊境牧羊犬見到芝娃娃身處險境，飛奔向牠，及時叼起牠跑開，免小狗被車輾死。<br />\n<br />\n女司機從倒後鏡見到有狗跑過，以為撞到牠們，落車一看，見到兩犬平安，才鬆一口氣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190415&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59489390\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190415%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59489390&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUatqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=5494a793\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190415%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59489390&h=1c04fcd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190415&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59489390</a><br />\n<br />\n隻牧羊犬真係好多事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a1a8e726716186039e4da76ac35ef08ba8ae54","tid":1107131,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T04:55:27.000Z","msg":"女司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35228db6a19df568e415cde934115f535341ba6","tid":1107131,"uid":54930,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"芝娃娃垃圾狗不救也罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6bc7ba98fd9b362152e4ee7b843af90995a87b4","tid":1107131,"uid":38518,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T04:57:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">馬上成為壹會員<br />\n會員專區 